data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom residence offering 2,347 square feet of luxurious living space on a generous 0.20-acre lot. Nestled in a serene neighborhood, this home features remarkable features and thoughtful design throughout. With decorative high ceilings, porcelain tile, granite countertops, and custom cabinets throughout, this home exudes sophistication. The open layout seamlessly connects living, dining, and kitchen spaces. A backyard that features a BBQ area, perfect for outdoor enjoyment. Conveniently situated by the expressway, this home combines luxury and accessibility. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity – arrange a viewing today and seize your chance to call this stunning property your new home!
